        <div class="content">
          <p class="h5"><a href="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/interviews/home-away-agn-s-varda">At home (and away) with Agnès Varda</a></p>
                      <p class="authors"> Daniel  Trilling  </p>
